WEBVTT

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:34.136
to Nishaat and Anya,
who are now 20 and 15 years old.

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:36.656
And these two roles have shown me that

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:40.256
we don’t teach children,
children teach us.

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:42.016
They show us a mirror in which

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:46.176
we clearly see
our own challenges and faults.

00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:48.536
And alongside they show us a way

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:53.616
to be better, sensitive,
and more aware human beings.

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:54.856
In today’s time,

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:57.376
when people can’t stop
talking to each other

00:01:57.400 --> 00:02:00.416
in the real or digital world,